      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Fried and Baptized",
        "Client": "Unflappable Biologist",
        "Description": "I tend to ignore these little \u0022tiffs\u0022\r\nbetween monsters while out in\r\nthe field. Especially since I have\r\na special cloak to protect me. But\r\nit becomes increasingly difficult to\r\nignore when the forest is flooding\r\nand burning at the same time...",
